Interface IdContainer

All Known Implementing Classes:
SVG12OMDocument, SVGOMDocument, SVGOMUseShadowRoot, XBLOMShadowTreeElement
public interface IdContainer

An interface for DOM nodes that can look up elements with IDs. This is used to give common interface to Document and XBLShadowTreeElement objects.
